"The Michelin gastronomic guide freezes work on all its projects in Russia." Trucker Timur, snacking on delicious shawarma in a roadside cafe, accountant of the medical unit Semyon Ignatievich, who took carrot salad and buckwheat with a cutlet in the factory canteen, student Lyuba, chatting with her friends over a cappuccino from " Coffee to go" - all of them will no longer be able to live their former carefree life, knowing that their restaurants will not receive a "Mischlen" star.